title: Grateful Dead Live at Red Rocks Ampitheatre on 1984-06-12
lineage: Nakamichi MR2 > Marantz PMD661|SD >WIN10 Audacity|cdwav|TLH Flac level8
taper: Executive Crew Chris Kidwell, Sean Murtha, Tom Pinney, Kyle Holbrook
description:
Set I
Alabama Getaway > Greatest Story Ever Told, Friend Of The Devil, Little Red Rooster, Big Railroad Blues, Me & My Uncle > Mexicali Blues, Althea, Looks Like Rain, Might As Well

Set II
Scarlet Begonias > Touch Of Grey > Estimated Prophet > Eyes Of The World > Drums > Space > The Other One > Wharf Rat > Around & Around > Johnny B. Goode

Encore:
U.S. Blues

Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
